The study is both qualitative and quantitative, gathering patient's perceptions of HCV treatment benefits before and after HCV treatment by administering surveys and conducting in-depth qualitative patient interviews.

 The study seeks to understand all anticipated and actual benefits patients perceive before and after viral eradication.

